    dc:description "FIGURES 2. Paederus brunneolus sp. nov. from Xinjiang. A. habitus; B. aedeagus, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, lateral view; D. aedeagus, ventral view; E. sternite VIII, female; F. sternite IX, female. Scale bars: A = 1 mm; B – E = 0.5 mm; F = 0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230887/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230886>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1. Paederus bilobus sp. nov. from Hainan. A. habitus; B. aedeagus, ventral view; E. aedeagus, lateral view 1; D. aedeagus, dorsal view; E. sternite VIII, female; F. sternite IX, female; G. aedeagus, lateral view 2. Scale bars: A = 1 mm; B – E, G = 0.5 mm; F = 0.25 mm." ;
